text: Stéphanie Bannwart (born 11 January 1991) is a Swiss volleyball player. She played at the 2008 Junior European Championships, 2013 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2013 CEV Volleyball European Championship. She played for VB Therwil and Sm'Aesch Pfeffingen. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss volleyball players
